title: Robert Spillane on Tom Brady saying he doesn't have a dog in the fight: Makes me sick

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Robert Spillane on Tom Brady saying he doesn't have a dog in the fight: Makes me sick
sources.description: Tom Brady's feelings about Super Bowl LX didn't sit well with his former Patriots teammate Vince Wilfork and a current member of the team had a similar feeling about Brady's take.
